summary:
A small warriorhouse replacing the breezehome, has two cells:
Warriorhouse (the regular entrance) and the \"Dovakiin\'s Quarters\" which is in the left side of the home.
descriptionHtml:
A small warriorhouse replacing the breezehome, has two cells:
Warriorhouse (the regular entrance) and the \"Dovakiin\'s Quarters\" which is in the left side of the home.
The warriorhouse has:
Arcane enchanter
Alchemy lab
Grindstone
Table with food
A bed
Ysgramor statue ( actually it\'s the spawning spot. )
A chest with daedric weapons + armor.
The Dovakiin\'s quarter has: ( STILL WORKING ON IT )
A bed
A wardrobe
A table.
THIS IS MY FIRST MOD FOR SKYRIM. I STARTED YESTERDAY.
author: Tomercp
